Rassilon smiles at you and strikes a pose.

His scarlet tunic is cut loose across his shoulders and tight at the waist.
Trimmed with black leather along the seams and hem, it is laced up the front
with a snaking of silver chain.  A short black cape hangs elegantly over his
left shoulder, half-concealing his left arm.  His black trousers are buttoned
up the front with nacrestones, and his square-toed boots are of finely tooled
black leather.

